comments: Booker (PHX) is moving alongside Russell's (MIN) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Russell (MIN) is bracing for the contact from Booker (PHX) and releases away from the contact.
Towns (MIN) extends his hand forward and makes contact with Bridges' (PHX) head that affects his SQBR.
Towns (MIN) and Crowder (PHX) come together at the same spot and briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Crowder (PHX) places his hand momentarily on Towns' (MIN) hip and he immediately removes his hand as Towns moves to receive the pass.
Towns (MIN) is already in Paul's (PHX) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Booker (PHX) extends his arm forward and makes contact with Russell's (MIN) arm as he defends the shot.
Ayton (PHX) is already in McDaniels' (MIN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Beverley (MIN) places his hand momentarily on Booker's (PHX) hip and he removes his hand as they move up the lane line.
Towns (MIN) jumps to the side of Ayton (PHX) and marginal contact occurs as Ayton spins away from Towns.  Additionally, the contact occurs prior to Ayton's upward shooting motion.
Towns (MIN) brushes Ayton's (PHX) arm and marginal contact occurs as he defends the shot near the rim.
Ayton (PHX) brings his left arm towards Towns (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Towns contests the shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) is moving alongside Russell's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Booker (PHX) cleanly deflects the ball away from Towns (MIN).
Crowder (PHX) and Towns (MIN) come together at the same spot and incidental contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
McDaniels (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Ayton (PHX) during rebounding.
Paul (PHX) makes contact with Beverley's (MIN) arm during his rebound. Ayton (PHX) is called for the foul, but he does not make illegal contact with Beverley.
Towns (MIN) briefly grasps Ayton's (PHX) arm and releases his arm as they reach for the rebound.
Russell (MIN) is bracing for the contact from Booker (PHX) and releases away from the contact.
Booker (PHX) is drawn into the air by Russell (MIN) and Booker delivers contact as Russell is starting his upward shooting motion.
Edwards (MIN) moves laterally into Paul's (PHX) path and initiates body to body contact prior to making any contact with the ball.
Russell (MIN) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Crowder (PHX) briefly grasps Towns' (MIN) jersey during rebounding.
Edwards (MIN) commits a take foul on Crowder (PHX).
Crowder (PHX) avoids making contact with Beasley (MIN) as he defends the shot attempt.
